<text><body>
<lb n="0610c03" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0610c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0610c05" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1151</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0610c06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0610001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note>修習般若波羅蜜菩薩觀行念誦
<lb n="0610c07" ed="T"/>儀軌<note n="0610002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【甲】</note><app n="0610002"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0610c08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0610c09" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0610c10" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑑
<lb n="0610c11" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0610c12" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0610c13" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><lg xml:id="lgT20p0610c1301"><l>歸命般若母</l><l>清淨妙法身</l>
<lb n="0610c14" ed="T"/><l>我今依瑜伽</l><l>演說觀行法</l>
<lb n="0610c15" ed="T"/><l>運心遍法界</l><l>一切佛剎海</l>
<lb n="0610c16" ed="T"/><l>想身周圍遶</l><l>由是得解脫</l>
<lb n="0610c17" ed="T"/><l>想身遶諸佛</l><l>一一諸佛前</l>
<lb n="0610c18" ed="T"/><l>菩薩眾圍遶</l><l>持妙供養具</l>
<lb n="0610c19" ed="T"/><l>三世諸如來</l><l>及大菩薩眾</l>
<lb n="0610c20" ed="T"/><l>緣覺與聲聞</l><l>一切正法藏</l>
<lb n="0610c21" ed="T"/><l>皆悉盡無餘</l><l>遍想於己身</l>
<lb n="0610c22" ed="T"/><l>一切<note n="0610003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乃＝及【甲】，彼ィ【甲】</note><note n="0610003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝及【甲】，＝彼ィ【甲】</note><app n="0610003"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">及</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">彼</rdg></app>眾前</l><l>分明如對目</l>
<lb n="0610c23" ed="T"/><l>皆從淨心生</l><l>廣多供養具</l>
<lb n="0610c24" ed="T"/><l>作無量供養</l><l>無間<note n="0610004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恒＝應【甲】</note><app n="0610004"><lem wit="【大】">恒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">應</rdg></app>作禮</l>
<lb n="0610c25" ed="T"/><l>宮殿妙拂蓋</l><l>無數眾樓閣</l>
<lb n="0610c26" ed="T"/><l>花鬘末塗香</l><l>種種寶莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0610c27" ed="T"/><l>彼諸供養儀</l><l>遍滿虛空界</l>
<lb n="0610c28" ed="T"/><l>殷勤心加持</l><l>奉獻諸如來</l>
<lb n="0610c29" ed="T"/><l>如空剎土爾</l><l>如剎佛亦然</l>
<pb n="0611a" xml:id="T20.1151.0611a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0611a01" ed="T"/><note n="0611001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（如佛…量）十五字＝（佛法既無窮供養悉周遍一心恒供養）十五字ィ【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="15" n="0611001"><lem wit="【大】"><l>如佛法亦然</l><l>如法供養然</l>
<lb n="0611a02" ed="T"/><l>一切皆無量</l></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">佛法既無窮供養悉周遍一心恒供養</rdg></app><l>十方無邊剎</l>
<lb n="0611a03" ed="T"/><l>知已作是言</l><l><note n="0611002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">敬禮諸如來＝普禮佛法海ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611002"><lem wit="【大】">敬禮諸如來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">普禮佛法海</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0611a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611a0401">遍禮一切如來真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0611a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611a0501" cb:type="dharani">唵薩嚩怛他<note place="inline">去</note>蘖多<note place="inline">一</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>那滿<note n="0611003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曩＝娜ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611003"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">娜</rdg></app><note place="inline">上引</note>喃迦
<lb n="0611a06" ed="T"/>嚕<note place="inline">引</note>弭<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0611a07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611a0701"><l>種種勝無量</l><l>大乘經所說</l>
<lb n="0611a08" ed="T"/><l>陀羅尼佛心</l><l>殷勤應稱誦</l>
<lb n="0611a09" ed="T"/><l>當生淨信心</l><l>專注於一境</l>
<lb n="0611a10" ed="T"/><l>為諸有情類</l><l>觀察勝菩提</l>
<lb n="0611a11" ed="T"/><l>即當作偏袒</l><l>右膝而著地</l>
<lb n="0611a12" ed="T"/><l>誠心合掌住</l><l>應作如是言</l>
<lb n="0611a13" ed="T"/><l>自作教他作</l><l>或自他隨喜</l>
<lb n="0611a14" ed="T"/><l>由身口意罪</l><l>願諸佛哀愍</l>
<lb n="0611a15" ed="T"/><l>今生一億罪</l><l>乃至無始世</l>
<lb n="0611a16" ed="T"/><l>及當坐菩提</l><l>不復更違犯</l>
<lb n="0611a17" ed="T"/><l>如是勝懺悔</l><l>真實觀察故</l>
<lb n="0611a18" ed="T"/><l>以佛願智火</l><l>焚盡無有餘</l>
<lb n="0611a19" ed="T"/><l>能取及所取</l><l>一切皆唯心</l>
<lb n="0611a20" ed="T"/><l>佛剎等供養</l><l>能取所取意</l>
<lb n="0611a21" ed="T"/><l>菩薩住等引</l><l>見心如影像</l>
<lb n="0611a22" ed="T"/><l>能取想分別</l><l>安住於空性</l>
<lb n="0611a23" ed="T"/><l><note n="0611004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝一ヵ【甲】</note><app n="0611004"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark">一</rdg></app>性無性相</l><l>是名為空相</l>
<lb n="0611a24" ed="T"/><l>無性非無性</l><l>不離於一性</l>
<lb n="0611a25" ed="T"/><l>能所及供養</l><l>三種離分別</l>
<lb n="0611a26" ed="T"/><l>由無分別故</l><l>此供養為勝</l>
<lb n="0611a27" ed="T"/><l>如是勝供養</l><l>及以旋遶法</l>
<lb n="0611a28" ed="T"/><l>一切重罪咎</l><l><note n="0611005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">除滅皆＝滅盡令ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611005"><lem wit="【大】">除滅皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">滅盡令</rdg></app>無餘</l>
<lb n="0611a29" ed="T"/><l>貪性知無貪</l><l>即入貪性空</l>
<pb n="0611b" xml:id="T20.1151.0611b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0611b01" ed="T"/><l>瞋性知無瞋</l><l>即入瞋性空</l>
<lb n="0611b02" ed="T"/><l>癡性知無癡</l><l>即入癡性空</l>
<lb n="0611b03" ed="T"/><l>如是於諸惑</l><l>觀察實相理</l>
<lb n="0611b04" ed="T"/><l>有此智慧者</l><l>由空無分別</l>
<lb n="0611b05" ed="T"/><l>如蓮華處水</l><l>不著諸罪咎</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b0601">修行者作如是觀照。淨身心已即結三昧耶
<lb n="0611b07" ed="T"/>印。</p>
<lb n="0611b08" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611b0801"><l>二羽相交合</l><l>當安於心上</l>
<lb n="0611b09" ed="T"/><l>遍觀虛空佛</l><l>誦真言三遍</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b1001"><note n="0611006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔真言曰〕ィ－【甲】＊</note><app n="0611006"><lem wit="【大】">真言曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0611b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b1101" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0611007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔唵〕ィ－【甲】＊</note><app n="0611007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩日<note n="0611008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𠻴一＝囉二【甲】</note><note n="0611008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->𠻴一＝囉二【甲】</note>𠻴<note place="inline">一合引</note>惹禮</p>
<lb n="0611b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b1201">次結金剛縛。十度外相叉。密縛成印相。金剛
<lb n="0611b13" ed="T"/>縛真言。<app type="star" corresp="#0611006"><lem wit="【大】">真言曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0611b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b1401" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱</p>
<lb n="0611b15" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611b1501"><l>如前金剛縛</l><l>掣擊於心上</l>
<lb n="0611b16" ed="T"/><l>能滅諸結使</l><l>開顯解脫宮</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b1701"><note n="0611009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即當…曰）八字＝（字想安於二乳即誦開心真言每誦掣開心戶）十八字ィ【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0611009"><lem wit="【大】">即當誦開心真言曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">字想安於二乳即誦開心真言每誦掣開心戶</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0611b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b1801" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">吒半音呼</note></p>
<lb n="0611b19" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611b1901"><l>次結發智印</l><l>如前金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0611b20" ed="T"/><l>定慧入於掌</l><l>召入圓寂智</l>
<lb n="0611b21" ed="T"/><l><note n="0611010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">召入於＝即誦召入ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611010"><lem wit="【大】">召入於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦召入</rdg></app>種智</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b2201">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0611b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b2301" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0611007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>吠舍惡</p>
<lb n="0611b24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611b2401"><l>次結金剛拳</l><l>進力<note n="0611011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跓＝拄【甲】</note><app n="0611011"><lem wit="【大】">跓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">拄</rdg></app>禪<note n="0611012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智＋（以附拄心門）ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611012"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">智以附拄心門</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0611b25" ed="T"/><l>金剛身語意</l><l>密合不傾動</l></lg>
<lb n="0611b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b2601"><note n="0611013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即）ィ＋誦【甲】＊</note><app n="0611013"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦</rdg></app>金剛拳真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0611b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611b2701" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>畝瑟置<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0611014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𤚥＝鑁ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611014"><lem wit="【大】">𤚥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">鑁</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611b28" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611b2801"><l>即結三昧耶</l><l>自成普賢故</l>
<lb n="0611b29" ed="T"/><l><note n="0611015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">結已＝縛以ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611015"><lem wit="【大】">結已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">縛以</rdg></app>竪忍願</l><l>身處於月輪</l></lg>
<pb n="0611c" xml:id="T20.1151.0611c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0611c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c0101">即誦三昧耶真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0611c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c0201" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0611007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三麼野薩怛鑁<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0611c03" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611c0301"><l>次結大真誓</l><l>忍願<note n="0611016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝交ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611016"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">交</rdg></app>入縛</l>
<lb n="0611c04" ed="T"/><l>檀慧定智竪</l><l>二度三觸心</l>
<lb n="0611c05" ed="T"/><l>藏識厭離種</l><l>能除悲增長</l></lg>
<lb n="0611c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c0601"><note n="0611017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復當誦真言曰〕－【甲】</note><app n="0611017"><lem wit="【大】">復當誦真言曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0611c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c0701" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0611007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三麼野護素囉多薩怛鑁<note place="inline">三合</note></p>
<lb n="0611c08" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611c0801"><l>次應作辟除</l><l>結金剛藥叉</l>
<lb n="0611c09" ed="T"/><l>二羽金剛拳</l><l>檀慧進力屈</l>
<lb n="0611c10" ed="T"/><l>置於口兩頰</l><l>想身同彼尊</l>
<lb n="0611c11" ed="T"/><l>厲聲誦真言</l><l>左右而顧視</l></lg>
<lb n="0611c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c1201"><note n="0611018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即誦）ィ＋金【甲】＊</note><app n="0611018"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦金</rdg></app>剛藥叉真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0611c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c1301" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0611007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>藥乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>𤙖</p>
<lb n="0611c14" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611c1401"><l>所有諸障者</l><l>悉皆四馳散</l>
<lb n="0611c15" ed="T"/><l>二目想麼吒</l><l>轉如日月輪</l>
<lb n="0611c16" ed="T"/><l>止觀金剛拳</l><l>各安於二𦜮</l>
<lb n="0611c17" ed="T"/><l>隨日作旋視</l><l>以成十方界</l></lg>
<lb n="0611c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c1801"><app type="star" corresp="#0611013"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦</rdg></app>金剛眼真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0611c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c1901" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>瑟知<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note n="0611019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吒＋（半音呼）細註ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611019"><lem wit="【大】">吒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">吒<note place="inline">半音呼</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0611c20" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611c2001"><l>當入三摩地</l><l>縛印相如前</l>
<lb n="0611c21" ed="T"/><l>仰安結跏上</l><l>端身須正直</l>
<lb n="0611c22" ed="T"/><l>閉目入正定</l><l>遍觀虛空佛</l>
<lb n="0611c23" ed="T"/><l>盡滿如胡麻</l><l>彼一切如來</l>
<lb n="0611c24" ed="T"/><l>憶昔誓願故</l><l>異口同音聲</l>
<lb n="0611c25" ed="T"/><l>教授說真言</l><l><note n="0611020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">專注實相理＝加持修行者ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611020"><lem wit="【大】">專注實相理</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">加持修行者</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0611c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0611c2601" cb:type="dharani">唵薩嚩喻誐質多沒答跛<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0611021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">那＝娜ィ【甲】</note><app n="0611021"><lem wit="【大】">那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">娜</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">引</note>弭<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0611c27" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0611c2701"><l>專注實相理</l><l>頻誦此真言</l>
<lb n="0611c28" ed="T"/><l>安心內觀察</l><l>漸令周法界</l>
<lb n="0611c29" ed="T"/><l>一切虛空相</l><l>虛空亦無相</l>
<pb n="0612a" xml:id="T20.1151.0612a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0612a01" ed="T"/><l><note n="0612001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虛空瑜伽故＝真實瑜伽教ィ【甲】</note><app n="0612001"><lem wit="【大】">虛空瑜伽故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">真實瑜伽教</rdg></app></l><l>舒遍於十方</l></lg>
<lb n="0612a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a0201">行者既入。般若波羅蜜甚深體性三摩地。則
<lb n="0612a03" ed="T"/>於真實性中證大月輪量同法界。光明普照
<lb n="0612a04" ed="T"/>寂然清涼。起大悲愍一切有情三界熾然。如
<lb n="0612a05" ed="T"/>一子想深生拔濟。而作是念我今云何。<note n="0612002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔令〕－ヵ【甲】</note><app n="0612002"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>未
<lb n="0612a06" ed="T"/>得度而令得<note n="0612003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">度＋（者）ヵ【甲】</note><app n="0612003"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">度</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark">度者</rdg></app>。未解脫者令得解脫。未安慰
<lb n="0612a07" ed="T"/>者令得安慰。未涅槃者令得涅槃。則入本尊
<lb n="0612a08" ed="T"/>瑜伽三摩地。觀身為般若波羅蜜佛母。戴五
<lb n="0612a09" ed="T"/>佛冠天衣瓔珞。金色光明遍毛孔中。流出無
<lb n="0612a10" ed="T"/>量諸佛。又作是念。我身與般若波羅蜜菩薩
<lb n="0612a11" ed="T"/>無二無別。即以金剛護菩薩加持四處。</p>
<lb n="0612a12" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0612a1201"><l>二羽金剛縛</l><l>進力竪如針</l>
<lb n="0612a13" ed="T"/><l>印心頞喉頂</l><l>成本尊瑜伽</l></lg>
<lb n="0612a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a1401">即誦<note n="0612004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（金剛護）ィ＋真【甲】</note><app n="0612004"><lem wit="【大】">真</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">金剛護真</rdg></app>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a1501" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0612a16" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0612a1601"><l>次結五佛冠</l><l>二手金剛縛</l>
<lb n="0612a17" ed="T"/><l>忍願形如刀</l><l>進力附上節</l>
<lb n="0612a18" ed="T"/><l>置頂次四方</l><l>二拳額前遶</l>
<lb n="0612a19" ed="T"/><l>如鬘頂後繫</l><l>垂下勢如帶</l></lg>
<lb n="0612a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2001"><note n="0612005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即誦）ィ＋一【甲】</note><app n="0612005"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦一</rdg></app>切如來寶冠真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2101" cb:type="dharani">唵部<note n="0612006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欠＋（平）細註ィ【甲】</note><app n="0612006"><lem wit="【大】">欠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">欠<note place="inline">平</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0612a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2201">次誦金剛部真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2301" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛嚩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0612a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2401">次誦寶部真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2501" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛娜<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0612a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2601">次誦蓮華部真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2701" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達囉摩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0612a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2801">次誦事業部真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612a2901" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>羯囉磨<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<pb n="0612b" xml:id="T20.1151.0612b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0612b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b0101">次誦金剛鬘灌頂真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b0201" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note>邏<note place="inline">引</note>避詵者<note place="inline">二</note>滿<note place="inline">三引</note>𤚥</p>
<lb n="0612b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b0301">次結甲冑印。二羽金剛印。擐甲及自他。頭指
<lb n="0612b04" ed="T"/>相繞結。恒成於大護。即誦甲冑真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b0501" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0612007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（嚩日…唅）二十一字＝（砧）一字ィ【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="21" n="0612007"><lem wit="【大】">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦嚩左嚩日𠼝<note place="inline">二合</note>句嚕嚩日
<lb n="0612b06" ed="T"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>唅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">砧</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0612b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b0701">以此甲冑印及誦真言而被甲。即得金剛性
<lb n="0612b08" ed="T"/>身。及獲金剛壽命。盡形得大加護。於一切處
<lb n="0612b09" ed="T"/>無能沮壞。被甲已齊。掌拍令歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0612b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b1001"><note n="0612008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝即ィ【甲】</note><app n="0612008"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即</rdg></app>誦金剛歡喜真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b1101" cb:type="dharani">嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0612009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕ィ－【甲】＊</note><app n="0612009"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一</note>都使野<note place="inline">二合二</note>斛<note place="inline">三</note></p>
<lb n="0612b12" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0612b1201"><l>由此心真言</l><l>解縛得歡喜</l>
<lb n="0612b13" ed="T"/><l>獲得金剛體</l><l>如金剛薩埵</l>
<lb n="0612b14" ed="T"/><l>遍入金剛已</l><l>大印如儀則</l>
<lb n="0612b15" ed="T"/><l>身前應當結</l><l>思惟大薩埵</l>
<lb n="0612b16" ed="T"/><l>見彼智薩埵</l><l>應觀於自身</l>
<lb n="0612b17" ed="T"/><l>鉤召引入縛</l><l>令喜作成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0612b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b1801">即誦般若波羅蜜遍入真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b1901" cb:type="dharani">唵達麼嚩日<note n="0612010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝哩ィ【甲】</note><app n="0612010"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">哩</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0612011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡＝噁ィ【甲】</note><app n="0612011"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">噁</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0612b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b2001">次誦般若波羅蜜觀念心真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b2101" cb:type="dharani">唵達麼嚩日㘑<note place="inline">二合</note>涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>捨野<note place="inline">二合</note>弱吽鑁
<lb n="0612b22" ed="T"/>斛</p>
<lb n="0612b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612b2301"><note n="0612012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（印契如前相觀身同本尊）ィ＋此【甲】</note><app n="0612012"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">印契如前相觀身同本尊此</rdg></app>是大薩埵鉤召引入縛令心喜悅<app type="star" corresp="#0611013"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦</rdg></app>三昧
<lb n="0612b24" ed="T"/>耶薩怛鑁<note place="inline">三合</note>遍入背後而月輪。於中應觀
<lb n="0612b25" ed="T"/><note n="0612013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔後面〕ィ－【甲】</note><app n="0612013"><lem wit="【大】">後面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>薩埵。我三昧耶薩怛鑁<note place="inline">三合</note>隨彼印薩
<lb n="0612b26" ed="T"/>埵。修習觀自身。金剛語已成。能成就諸印。行
<lb n="0612b27" ed="T"/>者即於壇中本尊像前。想七寶樓閣而開四
<lb n="0612b28" ed="T"/>門。於其殿中觀地字門。成般若波羅蜜佛母。
<lb n="0612b29" ed="T"/>以十波羅蜜圍遶。及八供養四門鉤鎖并八
<pb n="0612c" xml:id="T20.1151.0612c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0612c01" ed="T"/>方天眾。皆以本種子字觀想而成。復想己身
<lb n="0612c02" ed="T"/>在於色界阿迦尼吒天。即當作請印。</p>
<lb n="0612c03" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0612c0301"><l>召集作彈指</l><l>應請一切佛</l>
<lb n="0612c04" ed="T"/><l>剎那頃諸佛</l><l>并金剛菩薩</l>
<lb n="0612c05" ed="T"/><l>應滿一切壇</l><l>集會曼茶羅</l>
<lb n="0612c06" ed="T"/><l>即速疾大印</l><l>觀金剛薩埵</l>
<lb n="0612c07" ed="T"/><l>一遍稱百八</l><l>由結集印喜</l>
<lb n="0612c08" ed="T"/><l>如來皆堅固</l><l>金剛薩自成</l>
<lb n="0612c09" ed="T"/><l>慈友而安住</l><l>諸門一切處</l>
<lb n="0612c10" ed="T"/><l>鉤等而作業</l><l>以大羯磨印</l></lg>
<lb n="0612c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612c1101"><note n="0612014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（即誦）ィ＋召【甲】</note><app n="0612014"><lem wit="【大】">召</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦召</rdg></app>集真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612c1201" cb:type="dharani">唵嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>三麼野惹弱</p>
<lb n="0612c13" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0612c1301"><l>次當結四攝</l><l>二羽金剛拳</l>
<lb n="0612c14" ed="T"/><l>交腕結檀慧</l><l>頭指如大鉤</l>
<lb n="0612c15" ed="T"/><l>如索亦如鎖</l><l>手背而相<note n="0612015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">逼＋（次腕合而振禪智入於掌）ィ【甲】</note><app n="0612015"><lem wit="【大】">逼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">逼次腕合而振禪智入於掌</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0612c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612c1601"><app type="star" corresp="#0611018"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦金</rdg></app>剛鉤真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0612c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612c1701" cb:type="dharani">嚩日𠻴<note place="inline">二合</note>矩勢<note place="inline">一</note>弱</p>
<lb n="0612c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0612c1801"><app type="star" corresp="#0611018"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即誦金</rdg></app>剛索真言曰。</p>
